o, I will refrain."},{"chara":[{"id":101301}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"I will exhaust not a single one and@leave them all to Iroha's team!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":300401,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sasara","textRight":"Besides, wasn't that the last Witch around here?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":300401}],"flashEffect":"flashWhiteSlow2","se":"7211_souljem_02","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":300401,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":101301,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Sasara","textRight":"Yep, no more reactions."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":300601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Emiri","textRight":"Everyone else in the Union"},{"chara":[{"id":300601}],"nameRight":"Emiri","textRight":"must have taken out the Witches in their areas..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":300601,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Emiri","textRight":"Oh? Is our part done already then?"},{"chara":[{"id":101301,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"Let's ask Iroha if there are any@other troubles to take care of."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":101301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":401}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Wha― Every single witch in the shopping district?!","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100100,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Thank you so much!@You really helped us out!"},{"chara":[{"id":101301,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"Nothing but a trifle!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Well then, I'm sorry to ask for so much,"},{"chara":[{"id":100100}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"but I do have another request..."},{"chara":[{"id":101301,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"It's fine! Please don't hold back and tell me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp3.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Right now, Mikage is carrying out her idea,"},{"chara":[{"id":100100}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"\"Operation Friendship\" as she calls it."},{"chara":[{"id":100100}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"She went on a petition site to make this@\"Student Conference for the Future of Kamihama\"..."},{"chara":[{"id":100100}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Which is essential for the operation to succeed."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"Oh ho."},{"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"So I would like everyone to spread@the word about this site."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
